
<div>
  <h1 style="color: #3333CC;">Hi there, I'm DJ.</h1>
  <h2>I'm a <a href="/projects">web developer</a> looking for a company that is passionate about creative, self-motivated individuals.
  <br><br>
  I want to do great work while making the tech industry a more diverse, empathetic place.</h2>
